pedia.org/wiki/Heinrich_Karlen", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "126695121"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q124838", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/027453/2012-12-18"}